description:
Timothy Simons [Veep, Christine, The Boss, HouseBroken] and Anna talk about a raccoon threesome, twins, high school, first loves, break-ups, childbirth and more. Later in the episode Anna and Timothy offer their best Unqualified advice to a listener going through divorce and wondering how to get back into the dating scene. Their next call is with a listener who questions why her friends take so long responding to texts despite being glued to their phones.

Check out Second in Command: A Veep Rewatch with podcast hosts Matt Walsh and Timothy Simons.

Order Dealbreakers now. On sale wherever books are sold.

State Farm Like a good neighbor, State Farm is there. Call or go to statefarm.com for a quote today.

Skylight Frames Now, as a special offer, you can get $10 off your purchase of a Skylight Frame when you go skylightframe.com and enter code FARIS. That’s right. To get $10 off your purchase of a Skylight Frame just go skylightframe.com and enter code FARIS.

Living Proof Put the science to work and unlock your hair’s full potential with Living Proof like I did. Visit livingproof.com/ANNA and use code ANNA to get ten percent off your first purchase. That’s livingproof.com/ANNA, code ANNA for ten percent off your first purchase.

Masterclass Get unlimited access to EVERY MasterClass, and as an Anna Faris Is Unqualified listener, you get 15% off an annual membership! Go to masterclass.com/ANNA. 

McDonald's Wherever your local McDonald’s is, there’s nothing better than that wonderful feeling of community… well, maybe that great feeling is tied with eating a Big Mac. McDonald’s – I’m lovin’ it.

Netflix New episodes of Now Listen drop every other Thursday.  Subscribe now wherever you get your podcasts and follow @strongblacklead on all the socials to stay up-to-date.
